    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I reopened that because I detected that with Range slider based on [rheostat](https://github.com/airbnb/rheostat) is not possible handle `float` values.\r\n\r\nFor avoid that, I updated my current component implementation using `Math.trunc` to be ensure values are not floats: https://github.com/windtoday/windtoday-marketplace/commit/31f996ba3307ad2f4b040e60b6e35ae83239d701\r\n\r\nAlso [I answered in the rheostat repository](https://github.com/airbnb/rheostat/issues/67), I'm waiting response. I suppose handling float are not implemente based on the case of use of the component (just for price).\r\n\r\nI suppose that you are interested in update your component example @mthuret 😄 ",
